Supported Platforms
-------------------

Windows 7 (with Qt 4.7.0)
Ubuntu Linux 10.04 (with Qt 4.7.0)


Build Instructions
------------------

1. Have a working Qt 4.7.0 development environment.
2. Change to build directory:

    $ cd build

3. Generate the Makefile:

    $ qmake BOI.pro

4. Run make:

    For Ubuntu Linux:

        $ make

    For Windows 7:

        > nmake

The executable will be placed in the bin directory.

NOTE: On Ubuntu Linux it may be necessary to update the 
LD_LIBRARY_PATH environmental variable to point to the
{BOI Root}/lib directory.

